SELECT h.provider_name, h.specialty, COUNT(hr.record_id) AS total_visits FROM healthcare_providers h JOIN health_records hr ON h.provider_id = hr.provider_id GROUP BY h.provider_name, h.specialty ORDER BY total_visits DESC;

SELECT p.patient_id, p.age, h.provider_name, hr.visit_date, hr.diagnosis FROM population_health_data p JOIN health_records hr ON p.patient_id = hr.patient_id JOIN healthcare_providers h ON hr.provider_id = h.provider_id WHERE p.age > 50 ORDER BY hr.visit_date ASC;
